<description>
<![CDATA[TBI update :’) I suppose no one goes through life unscathed but this sucksssss. I often feel crazy because I’ll have a great week, feel relatively “normal” and get amped about work and my future etc. then I get hit with a week like this and have terrible migraines, can’t stop reflecting on my symptoms etc. recovery is a rollercoaster for sure (and exhausting) Anyways.. I hope this wasn’t too heavy but anyone who’s going through something similar just know you’re not alone ❤️
