<title><![CDATA[Everything i grilled for my friends while camping this weekend !...]]></title>
<link>https://prank-arum.github.io/Feeds/TikTok/susi.vidal/7613223197974023455.mp4</link>
<guid>https://tiktok.com/embed/7613223197974023455</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[Everything i grilled for my friends while camping this weekend !! I definitely want to emphasize I did not do this on my own lmaooo a ton of them helped grill, make drinks, and set up! It was a blast and we ate everything!! Zero leftovers 😎 Dinner details:  -chips, pico, and guac  -corn and flour tortillas  -carne asada and chicken tacos  -taco toppings: cilantro, onion, tomato, cotija cheese, lime  -grilled squash and onions (I was going for calabacitas vibes, I added olive oil, salt, oregano and cumin!)  -grilled corn (salt and butter)  -grilled Anaheim peppers (oil and salt)  -chipotle crema and lime/garlic/cilantro crema **had a late appearance to the party lmaoo
